<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jobbin Privacy Policy</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto py-8 px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>
                
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Introduction</h2>
                        <p>Thank you for choosing to use Jobbin. I am committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. If you have any questions or concerns about my policy or my practices with regards to your personal information, please contact me at anirudhananth99@gmail.com.</p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Information I Collect</h2>
                        <p>I collect personal information that you voluntarily provide when you use my services. The personal information I collect may include:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                            <li>Name and email address</li>
                            <li>Job application data such as job title, company, position, and location</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">3. How I Use Your Information</h2>
                        <p>I use the information I collect for various purposes, including:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                            <li>To provide and maintain my services</li>
                            <li>To provide customer support</li>
                            <li>To monitor the usage of my services</li>
                            <li>To detect, prevent and address technical issues</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">4. How I Store Your Information</h2>
                        <p>I use Supabase, a secure cloud database service, to store your personal information. Supabase employs industry-standard security measures to protect your data. Your information is stored on secure servers and is only accessed when necessary to provide my services to you.</p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">5. How I Share Your Information</h2>
                        <p>I do not share your personal information with third parties. Your data is only used to provide and improve the Jobbin service.</p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">6. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>
                        <p>You have certain data protection rights. If you wish to be informed what personal data I hold about you and if you want it to be removed from my systems, please contact me. Your rights include:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                            <li>The right to access, update or delete the information I have on you</li>
                            <li>The right of rectification</li>
                            <li>The right to object</li>
                            <li>The right of restriction</li>
                            <li>The right to data portability</li>
                            <li>The right to withdraw consent</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                        <p>I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy.</p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">8. Contact Me</h2>
                        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact me by email: anirudhananth99@gmail.com</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>